column2: SELECT    m.objid,m.Column1 as objid2, m.ra1 AS ra1, m.dec1 AS dec1,    m.apstar_id, m.apogee_id, a.apstar_id, params.*, paramerrs.*, elemsALL.* into mydb.apogeestar_photobj_aspcap from mydb.apogeestar_photobj AS m     JOIN aspcapStar AS a ON m.apstar_id =a.apstar_id   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParams(a.aspcap_id) params CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParamErrs(a.aspcap_id) paramerrs   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElemsAll( a.aspcap_id ) elemsALL
